        Ashes of Elrant DLC
      </h2>
      <p class="dlc-card-description">
        A separate standalone guide for all Ashes of Elrant DLC content, with
        its own walkthrough, sidequests, reward boards, and guides — tracked
        independently from the main game.
      </p>
      <a
